---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI & Intelligent Automation Services"
  description="Custom AI tools integrated into operations. GenAI internal tools, AI assistants, agent workflows, and knowledge retrieval systems for UK SMEs."
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-blue bg-brand-blue-pale px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Typical timeline: 3–6 weeks</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate">AI & Intelligent Automation</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-slate-light">
        Custom AI tools integrated into your operations. From intelligent assistants to automated knowledge retrieval—bringing advanced capabilities within reach of growing businesses.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-light">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate">The Opportunity</h2>
        <p>
          AI is no longer just for tech giants. The tools exist to build intelligent systems that work for SMEs—but most businesses don't know where to start:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Generic AI tools don't understand your business context</li>
          <li>Enterprise AI solutions are priced for corporations</li>
          <li>DIY approaches consume time without delivering results</li>
          <li>The gap between AI hype and practical value feels unbridgeable</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">What We Build</h2>
        <div class="not-prose grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">GenAI Internal Tools</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">Custom AI tools trained on your business data—for content generation, analysis, and decision support.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">AI Assistants</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">Intelligent assistants that understand your processes and help your team work faster.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">Agent Workflows</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">Automated workflows that use AI to handle complex, multi-step tasks with human oversight.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate">Knowledge Retrieval</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-light text-sm">AI-powered search and retrieval across your documents, databases, and institutional knowledge.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Our Approach</h2>
        <p>
          We focus on practical AI that solves real problems:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Business-first:</strong> We start with your workflows, not the technology</li>
          <li><strong>Right-sized:</strong> Solutions scaled to your needs and budget</li>
          <li><strong>Integrated:</strong> AI that works with your existing systems</li>
          <li><strong>Maintainable:</strong> Tools your team can use without data science expertise</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate mt-12">Technology</h2>
        <p>
          We use modern AI frameworks including large language models, embeddings, and retrieval-augmented generation—chosen based on your specific needs. Everything is built with security, privacy, and maintainability in mind.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="Ready to explore AI for your business?"
    description="Book a discovery call to discuss how intelligent automation could work for your operations."
  />
</BaseLayout>
